INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS: Extract cstrike -folder to X:\Program Files\Valve\Steam\SteamApps\<Your Steam Account>\counter-strike source (Where the "X" is your drive)

DESCRIPTION: Fightyard map on the rooftop. Just defeat your enemy.. Also you can access to another roof by walking through "bridges" and I think you don't want to fall on the street, because it's long way down.. :D
